Answer.translation3: Also a special lawyer has been appointed on behalf of the accused for the case.
Answer.translation4: Ajmal is in the police custody currently and it is expected that the police may be filing a charge sheet against him before January 24.
Answer.seg1: ممبئی حملے، شنوائی کے لیے سپیشل جج
Answer.translation5: The Ajmal asks for a lawyer to defend himself.

Answer.translation6: He has sent an appeal letter to the Pakistan government asking for legal Help.

Answer.translation7: It is said that evidences are available to say that Pakistani extremists has some relations with the attacks of Mumbai, India.

Answer.translation13: Lawyers from opposition political party have been protesting against this.

Input.seg4: ادھر واشنگٹن میں منگل کو نئے صدر کی تقریبِ حلفِ صدارت کے موقع پر عوام کے فقید المثال اجتماع کی تیاریاں کی جا رہی ہیں۔
Input.seg5: توقع ہے کہ صدر کے اس تاریخی حلفِ صدارت کو دیکھنے کے لیے بیس لاکھ کے قریب افراد واشنگٹن میں جمع ہوں گے۔
